  "prompt": "What is the best way to make your girlfriend happy when she is upset?",
  "response": "Here are some helpful ways to support your girlfriend when she's upset:\n\n1. Listen actively and empathetically\n- Give her your full attention\n- Let her express her feelings without judgment\n- Ask how you can support her\n\n2. Show emotional support\n- Be patient and understanding\n- Validate her feelings\n- Offer comfort and reassurance\n\n3. Practical steps\n- Ask if she wants to talk about what's bothering her\n- Offer a hug if she wants physical comfort\n- Give her space if she needs it\n\n4. Additional gestures\n- Spend quality time together\n- Do something thoughtful for her\n- Help her with tasks or chores\n- Bring her favorite food or treat\n\n5. Communication\n- Be gentle and caring\n- Avoid trying to \"fix\" everything immediately\n- Show genuine concern\n- Ask what she needs from you\n\n6. Specific actions\n- Offer to listen\n- Hold her hand\n- Help distract her if she wants\n- Be supportive without being pushy\n\nRemember that every person is different, so the most important thing is to understand her specific needs and preferences.",
